 标题：狮子（lion）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：אֲרִי, אַרְיֵה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：’ari, ’aryeh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:9\">GEN 49:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:9\">GEN 49:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num23:24\">NUM 23:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:9\">NUM 24:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:22\">DEU 33:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:5\">JDG 14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:8\">JDG 14:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:8\">JDG 14:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:9\">JDG 14:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:18\">JDG 14:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:34\">1SA 17:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:36\">1SA 17:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:37\">1SA 17:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:23\">2SA 1:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:10\">2SA 17:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:20\">2SA 23:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:20\">2SA 23:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:29\">1KI 7:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:29\">1KI 7:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:36\">1KI 7:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:19\">1KI 10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:20\">1KI 10:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:24\">1KI 13:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:24\">1KI 13:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:25\">1KI 13:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:26\">1KI 13:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:28\">1KI 13:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:28\">1KI 13:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:36\">1KI 20:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:36\">1KI 20:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:25\">2KI 17:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:26\">2KI 17:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.